snippet.title: Season 9 Hidden Alliance Overview Trailer : Tom Clancy’s The Division 2 - Warlords of New York
snippet.description:
Play Season 9 : Hidden Alliance on May 12th !
Featuring a new game mode with a race against time and enemies, you'll also have to fight Captain Lewis and his true sons. 

Warlords of New York is available on PC, PlayStation 4 and Xbox One.
